quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  29,64,"ЖҠam nguurndam aduna wonaali, si wanaa mbeleeЙ—e e fijindaaru. Pellet, ko hoЙ—o laakara ngon woni nguurandam. Sinno Й“e annduno"
  29,65,"Si Й“e waЙ—Й—ike ka laana, Й“e nodda Alla Й“e laЙ“Й“inano Mo noddaandu ndun. Tuma nde O daЙ—ndi Й“e ka njorndi, ontuma Й“e sirka"
  29,66,"No Й“e yeddira ko Men okki Й“e kon, awa yo Й“e dakmito! Aray kaЙ“e annda"
  29,67,"E Й“ee yi'aali wonnde Men waЙ—ii hormorde hoolniinde, yimЙ“e Й“en no cifee(bifte) bannge maЙ“Й“e? E ko meere nden Й“e gomЙ—inta Й“e yedda neemaaji Alla Й—in"
  29,68,"E ko hommbo Й“uri tooГұirde wa on fefindiiЙ—o fenaande e hoore Alla, maa o fenni goonga kan nde ka arunoo e makko? E wonaa ka Jahannama woni jaaЖҙorde yedduЙ“e Й“en"
  29,69,"ЖҒen tiiЙ—norЙ“e e (weltingol) Men, ma Men fewnirЙ“e e laawi Amen, ko pellet, Alla no wonndi e moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“en"